# Workflow

- Use red/green TDD for behavior changes.
- Write/adjust tests before implementation.
- Use platform primitives for DB and outbound calls.
- Run definition-of-done checks before claiming completion.

# Definition Of Done

- `make test`
- `make lint`
- `make typecheck`
- `make security`
